simple_step python API examples
-------------------------------

The examples currently focus on the high-level class methods of
Simple_Step: move_by, move_to_pos, soft_ramp_to_pos, set_vel_and_dir,
and soft_ramp_to_vel.

In addition examples of the the low level class methods stop, enable, 
disbale, get_dir, get_pos, set_zero_pos are also given.

For documentation on the low level class methods see the source code
simple_step/simple_step.py.

For examples demonstrating the the use of the low level class methods
see the implementation of the high level methods in
simple_step/simple_step.py.